\fs28 \cf0 Core Philosophy\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 The Values Ecosystem is not a course.\
It is not a sequence of lessons.\
It is not something students complete.\
It is a living world that students explore throughout their university experience\'97and perhaps throughout life.\
Students enter wherever curiosity, struggle, or interest leads them.\
Some habitats may be visited once.\
Others may become familiar places students return to repeatedly.\
There is no required path.\
There is no finish line.\
There is only exploration.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
