\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Learning to recognize fear without allowing it to become the ecosystem's dominant force.\
Fear has an important purpose, but it often becomes overactive, inaccurate, or unnecessarily controlling. Fear Woods teaches students how to evaluate fear rather than automatically obey it.\
