\f0\b\fs48 \cf0 \strokec2 THE LIVING GEOGRAPHY\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 How Values Shape the Ecosystem\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Unlike emotions, values are not habitats.\
They are the enduring landscape that gives shape, stability, nourishment, and direction to the entire ecosystem.\
Just as mountains influence rivers, forests, climate, and wildlife, our values influence how emotions develop, how we respond to challenges, and the direction our lives gradually take.\
Students never complete values.\
They continually orient themselves toward them.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa321\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs48 \cf0 \strokec2 The Purpose of the Living Geography\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 1. Orientation\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Values answer:\
"What kind of person do I want to become?"\
Emotions provide information.\
Values provide direction.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 2. Stability\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Emotions naturally change.\
Values remain comparatively stable.\
Like mountains that remain through changing weather, they provide dependable landmarks students can always return to.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 3. Nourishment\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Values nourish emotional growth.\
Compassion softens anger.\
Integrity gives courage direction.\
Authenticity strengthens love.\
Growth encourages resilience.\
